countless admonitions

00:29:12.740 --> 00:29:15.870
from the apostle Paul
and in the other letters.

00:29:15.870 --> 00:29:18.580
But in the Gospels,
from the voice of Jesus,

00:29:18.580 --> 00:29:23.470
we hear that his
reply to this question

00:29:23.470 --> 00:29:25.950
about what the greatest
of commandments is.

00:29:25.950 --> 00:29:28.440
