sexual ethics looks like.

00:29:58.070 --> 00:30:01.020
What are the things that help
us in all our relationships

00:30:01.020 --> 00:30:03.400
to fulfill these commandments?

00:30:03.400 --> 00:30:07.000
How do you love God, and
yourself, and your neighbor

00:30:07.000 --> 00:30:08.961
as best you can?

00:30:08.961 --> 00:30:09.460
Thank you.

